history.content:
Berkeley Engineers and Mentors (BEAM), ANova, Pioneers in Engineering (PiE), Sage Mentorship, and The Music Connection (TMC) are excited to invite you to a collaborative speaker series this Thursday, 4/7/22 from 8-9 PM in Evans 10. Members from these mentorship organizations will share stories from mentoring Bay Area youth, things they've learned along the way, and ways for you to get involved in the future.

 

Facebook event link: https://fb.me/e/2vLC6di3f
history.subject: Berkeley Mentorship Clubs Speaker Series
